Catherine Burns https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Catherine_Burns 0 Catherine Burns (born September 24, 1945) is an American actress of stage, film, radio and television. She was nominated for an Academy Award for Best Supporting Actress for her performance in Last Summer (1969).
